      "text": "JSONL diload dan setiap conversation\ndi tokenize pakai tokenizer Qwen2.5. \n\n loss masking: loss cuma dihitung di\ntoken bagian assistant (solusi CoT),\nbukan bagian user (prompt soal). Jadi\nmodel belajar generate solusi, bukan\nngafal soal.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "SFYNXYzcMk25_T7SRHhWB",
      "originalText": "JSONL diload dan setiap conversation di tokenize pakai tokenizer Qwen2.5. \n\n loss masking: loss cuma dihitung di token bagian assistant (solusi CoT), bukan bagian user (prompt soal). Jadi model belajar generate solusi, bukan ngafal soal.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
