      "width": 454,
      "height": 156,
      "index": "c004",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "SKENARIO 1 — Preprocess terbaik\nStage: DATA -> train tiap varian\nVarian (uji 1 faktor):\n  - tingkat filter: rule / +validity / +dedup\n  - extract: simpel vs OCR+image\n  - normalisasi LaTeX: on / off\n  - soal gambar: buang vs OCR/VLM\nUkur: acc heldout",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "my1OyE6_N8uusGpM",
      "originalText": "SKENARIO 1 — Preprocess terbaik\nStage: DATA -> train tiap varian\nVarian (uji 1 faktor):\n  - tingkat filter: rule / +validity / +dedup\n  - extract: simpel vs OCR+image\n  - normalisasi LaTeX: on / off\n  - soal gambar: buang vs OCR/VLM\nUkur: acc heldout",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "boundElements": []
