      "height": 156,
      "index": "c006",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "SKENARIO 2 — Metode CoT\nStage: CoT synth -> train\nVarian (uji 1 faktor):\n  - teacher: R1-Distill / Qwen-Math / API\n  - gaya: CoT panjang vs ringkas\n  - filter solusi: semua vs benar saja\n  - jml CoT/soal: 1 / 4 / 8\nUkur: acc heldout",
